"executed. Therefore it is reasonable to make it possible to link Transition "
"Actions freely with Transitions to be able to reuse them."
msgstr ""
"正如你所见，相同的转换操作会在很多地方被执行。因此设计允许转换操作与转换自由"
"连接，是为了更好的复用资源。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:874
msgid "Activities"
msgstr "活动"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:876
msgid ""
"We chose the approach to see Activities as a basket which can contain one or "
"more Activity Dialogs."
msgstr ""
"我们选择将活动(Activities)看作一个篮子，这个篮子可以包含一个或多个活动对话框"
"(Activity Dialogs)。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:880
msgid ""
"Click on \"Activities\" in the \"Available Process Elements\", then click on "
"\"Create New Activity\"."
msgstr "点击“可用的流程元素”中的“活动”，接着点击“创建新活动”。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:885
msgid "Create New Activity button"
msgstr "创建新活动按钮"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:887
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/customization/pm-accordion-new-activity.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/customization/pm-accordion-new-activity.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:892
msgid ""
"In the opened popup screen fill the \"Activity Name\", then drag the "
"required Activity Dialogs from the \"Available Activity Dialogs\" pool, and "
"drop them into to the \"Assigned Activity Dialogs\" pool. This dialogs will "
"be presented (in the ticket zoom screen) in the same order as it is defined "
"on this screen translating from top to bottom, from left to right."
msgstr ""
"在打开的弹出屏幕中填写“活动名称”，然后仅需从“可用的活动对话框”池中拖动需要的"
"活动对话框，并放到“分配的活动对话框”池中即可。这些对话框会在工单详情屏幕按本"
"屏幕定义的从上到下、从左到右的顺序显示出来。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:899
msgid ""
"This order is specially important in the first Activity, since the first "
"Activity Dialog for this activity is the only one that is presented when the "
"process starts."
msgstr ""
"在第一个活动中这个顺序特别重要，因为流程开始后唯一显示的就是这个活动的第一个"
"活动对话框。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:903
msgid "Create the following Activities:"
msgstr "创建下列活动："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:908
msgid "\"Recording the demand\" (A1)"
msgstr "“记录需求” (A1)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:909
msgid "Contains the Activity Dialog \"Recording the demand\" (AD1)"
msgstr "包含活动对话框“记录需求” (AD1)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:912
msgid "\"Approval\" (A2)"
msgstr "“审批” (A2)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:914
msgid ""
"Contains the Activity Dialogs \"Approval denied\" (AD2) as well as \"Approved"
"\" (AD3)"
msgstr "包含活动对话框“审批拒绝” (AD2)和“通过审批” (AD3)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:919
msgid "\"Order\" (A3)"
msgstr "“订单” (A3)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:921
msgid ""
"Contains the Activity Dialogs \"Order rejected\" (AD4) as well as \"Order "
"placed\" (AD5)"
msgstr "包含活动对话框“采购拒绝” (AD4)与“生成订单” (AD5)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:926
msgid "\"Incoming\" (A4)"
msgstr "“即将到达” (A4)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:927
msgid "Contains the Activity Dialog \"Shipment received\" (AD6)"
msgstr "包含活动对话框“货品收到” (AD6)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:930
msgid ""
"\"Process complete\" (A5): This is an Activity without possible Activity "
"Dialogs.  It will be set after \"Approval denied\", \"Order denied\" or "
"\"Shipment received\" and represents the end of the process."
msgstr ""
"“流程结束” (A5): 这是一个没有活动对话框的活动。它需要被设置在“审批拒绝”、“采"
"购拒绝”或者“货品收到”之后，代表流程结束。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:939
msgid ""
"Now we can clearly see that Activities are precisely defined states of a "
"process ticket. After a successful Transition a process ticket moves from "
"one Activity to another."
msgstr ""
"现在我们可以清晰地看到，活动是一个流程工单精确定义的状态。在转换成功后，流程"
"工单会从一个活动移动到另外一个。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:945
msgid "Book ordering process Path"
msgstr "书籍采购流程路径"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:947
msgid ""
"Let us conclude our example with the last missing piece in the puzzle, the "
"Process as the a flow describer. In our case this is the whole ordering work-"
"flow. Other processes could be office supply ordering or completely "
"different processes."
msgstr ""
"让我们用拼图所缺失的最后一块来结束我们的示例-将流程作为流记录器。在我们的例子"
"中，就是完整的订购工作流。其他流程可能还有办公用品订购或其他完全不同的流程。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:952
msgid ""
"The process has a starting point which consists of the start Activity and "
"the start Activity Dialog. For any new book order, the start Activity Dialog "
"(first Activity Dialog for the first Activity) is the first screen that is "
"displayed. If this is completed and saved, the Process ticket will be "
"created and can follow the configured work-flow."
msgstr ""
"此流程有一个起始点，它包括了初始活动和初始活动对话框。对于任何新书采购，初始"
"活动对话框(第一个活动的第一个活动对话框)是最先显示的。如果这个活动完成并保"
"存，流程工单将被创建并可以根据配置好的工作流进行处理。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:959
msgid ""
"The process also contains the directions for how the process ticket can move "
"through the Process. Let's call this the \"Path\". It consists of the start "
"Activity, one or more Transitions (possibly with Transition Actions), and "
"other Activities."
msgstr ""
"流程中还包含了流程工单在流程中如何移动的方向。我们称之为“路径”。它由初始活"
"动、一个或多个转换(可能包含转换操作)、以及其他活动组成。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:964
msgid ""
"Assuming that the Activities has already assigned their Activity Dialogs "
"drag an Activity from the accordion (in the left part of the screen) and "
"drop it into the canvas area (below process information). Notice that an "
"arrow from the process start (green circle) to the Activity is placed "
"automatically. (This is the first Activity and its first Activity Dialog is "
"the first screen that will be shown when the process starts)."
msgstr ""
"假设该活动已经指派了相关的活动对话框，将其从折叠区域(屏幕的左侧部分)拖放到画"
"布区域(在流程信息下面)。请注意，流程起始(绿色圆圈)会自动放置一个到该活动的箭"
"头。(这是第一个活动，并且其第一个活动对话框会在流程开始后在屏幕第一个显示)。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:973
msgid "Drag first Activity into the canvas"
msgstr "将第一个活动拖放到画布中"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:975
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/customization/pm-canvas-drag-activity.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/customization/pm-canvas-drag-activity.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:980
msgid ""
"Next, drag another Activity into the canvas too. Now we will have two "
"Activities in the canvas. The first one is connected to the start point and "
"the second has no connections. You can hover the mouse over each activity to "
"reveal their own Activity Dialogs."
msgstr ""
"下一步，将另一个活动也拖放到画布中。现在画布中我们有了两个活动。第一个活动连"
"接到起始点，第二个活动还没有连接。你可以将鼠标移动到活动上，会显示它们自己的"
"活动对话框。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:987
msgid "Drag second Activity into the canvas"
msgstr "拖动第二个活动到画布中"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:989
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/customization/pm-canvas-drag-activity2.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/customization/pm-canvas-drag-activity2.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:994
msgid ""
"Then let's create the \"Path\" (connection) between this two Activities, for "
"this we will use the Transitions. Click on Transitions in the accordion drag "
"a Transition and drop it inside the first Activity. Notice that the Activity "
"changes its color indicating that the Transition is attached. As soon as the "
"Transition is dropped the end point of the Transition arrow will be placed "
"next to the process start point. Drag the Transition arrow end point and "
"drop it inside the other Activity to create the connection between the "
"Activities."
msgstr ""
"接下来让我们在这两个活动间创建“路径”（连接），创建路径需要使用转换。在折叠区"
"域点击“转换”并拖动一个转换到第一个活动里面放下。注意活动变化了颜色，表示附上"
"了转换。转换一放下，转换箭头的终点就放置在邻近流程的起始点位置。拖动转换的箭"
"头终点到另一活动里面来创建这两个活动的连接。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1004
msgid "Drag a Transition into the canvas"
msgstr "拖放一个转换到画布上"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1006
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/customization/pm-canvas-drag-transition.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/customization/pm-canvas-drag-transition.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1011
msgid ""
"Now that the \"Path\" between the Actions is defined, then we need to assign "
"the Transition Actions to the Transition, double click the Transition label "
"(in the canvas), this will open a new popup window."
msgstr ""
"现在操作之间的“路径”已经定义好了，接下来我们需要分配转换操作到这个转换上，在"
"画布中双击转换标签，这会弹出新屏幕。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1017
msgid "Connect Activities using Transitions"
msgstr "使用转换连接活动"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1019
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/customization/pm-canvas-drag-transition2.png"
"\" scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/customization/pm-canvas-drag-transition2.png"
"\" scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1024
msgid ""
"Drag the needed Transition Actions from Available Transition Actions pool "
"and drop them into the Assigned Transition Actions pool and click on submit "
"button."
msgstr ""
"从‘可用的转换操作’池中拖动所需的转换活动，并将其放置在‘分配的转换操作’池中，"
"点击提交按钮。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1029
msgid "Assign Transition Actions"
msgstr "分配转换操作"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1031
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/customization/pm-edit-path.png\" scalefit="
"\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/customization/pm-edit-path.png\" scalefit="
"\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1036
msgid ""
"Then back in the main process edit screen click on save button below the "
"canvas to save all other changes."
msgstr "接着回到流程编辑主屏幕，点击画布下的保存按钮，保存所有其他的修改。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1040
msgid ""
"Complete the \"path\" adding the following Activities, Transitions and "
"Transition Actions:"
msgstr "添加下列活动、转换和转换操作以完成“路径”："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1043
msgid "Recording the demand until \"Approval\""
msgstr "记录需求直到“批准”"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1047
msgid "Starting point: Activity: \"Recording the demand\" (A1)"
msgstr "起始点：活动“记录需求” (A1)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1050
msgid "Possible Transition: \"Approval\" (T1)"
msgstr "可能的转换：“审批” (T1)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1054
msgid ""
"If the condition of this activity is fulfilled, the ticket will move to "
"Activity: \"Approval\" (A2)"
msgstr "如果这个活动的条件满足，该工单将移动到活动“审批” (A2)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1060
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1105
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1183
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1256
msgid "Additionally, the following Transition Actions are executed:"
msgstr "此外，还会执行下列的转换操作："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1078
msgid ""
"The Activity: \"Recording the demand\" (A1) is a defined step of the process "
"ticket, where there is the possibility for the Transition: \"Approval"
"\" (T1). If this applies, the ticket will move to the next Activity: "
"\"Approval\" (A2), and the Transition Actions: \"Move the process ticket "
"into the 'Management' queue\" (TA1) and \"Change ticket responsible to "
"'manager'\" (TA2) are executed. In the Activity: \"Approval\" (A2), the "
"Activity Dialogs: \"Approval denied\" (AD2) and \"Approved\" (AD3) are "
"available."
msgstr ""
"活动：“记录需求” (A1)是流程工单预定义步骤，以确认转换：“审批” (T1)的可能性。"
"如果适用，工单将移动到下一个活动：“审批” (A2)，并且执行转换操作“移动到‘管"
"理’队列” (TA1)和“变更工单负责人为‘经理’ (TA2)。在活动“审批” (A2)中，活动对话"
"框“审批拒绝” (AD2) 和“通过审批” (AD3) 可用。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1089
msgid "Starting Point: Activity \"Approval\" (A2)"
msgstr "起始点：活动“审批” (A2)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1092
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1170
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1243
msgid "Possible Transitions:"
msgstr "可能的转换："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1099
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1177
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1250
msgid ""
"If this matches, the process ticket will move to Activity: \"Process complete"
"\" (A5)."
msgstr "如果匹配这个，流程工单就移动到活动“流程结束” (A5)。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1134
msgid ""
"If this matches, the process ticket will move to Activity: \"Order\" (A3)."
msgstr "如果匹配这个，流程工单就移动到活动“订购” (A3)。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1140
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1218
msgid "Additionally, the following Transition Action is executed:"
msgstr "此外，还会执行下面的转换操作：："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1159
msgid ""
"We can see that from the current Activity, which defines a step of the "
"process ticket, there are one or more possibilities for Transition which "
"have exactly one target Activity (and possibly one or more Transition "
"Actions)."
msgstr ""
"我们可以看到，定义流程工单的当前活动有一个或多个转换的可能性，转换有一个目标"
"活动（和可能的一个或多个转换操作）。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1167
msgid "Starting Point: Activity \"Order\" (A3)"
msgstr "起始点：活动“订购” (A3)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1195
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1267
msgid "\"Set ticket responsible to 'Employee'\" (TA4)"
msgstr "“设置工单负责人为‘员工’” (TA4)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1212
msgid ""
"If this matches, the process ticket will move to Activity: \"Incoming\" (A4)."
msgstr "如果匹配这个，流程工单就移动到活动“即将到达” (A4)。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1236
msgid "Incoming"
msgstr "即将到达"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1240
msgid "Starting Point: Activity \"Incoming\" (A4)"
msgstr "起始点：活动“即将到达” (A4)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1284
msgid ""
"The complete Path for the book ordering Process will then look like this:"
msgstr "书籍采购流程完整路径看上去就像这样："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1288
