msgstr "最后修改转换的时间。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2468
msgid "UID of the last user who changed this Transition."
msgstr "最后修改转换的用户UID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2472
msgid "Condition"
msgstr "条件"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2474
msgid ""
"Contains all conditions that are necessary for this Transition to take "
"effect.  Example:"
msgstr "包含这个转换生效所需的所有条件。例如："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2479
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Condition => {\n"
"    Type  => 'and',\n"
"    Cond1 => {\n"
"        Type   => 'and',\n"
"        Fields => {\n"
"            StateID => {\n"
"                Type  => 'String',\n"
"                Match => '1',\n"
"            },\n"
"            DynamicField_Marke => {\n"
"                Type  => 'String',\n"
"                Match => 'VW',\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"    Cond2 => {\n"
"        Type => 'and',\n"
"        Fields => {\n"
"            Queue => {\n"
"                Type  => 'String',\n"
"                Match => 'Raw',\n"
"            },\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"},\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"Condition => {\n"
"    Type  => 'and',\n"
"    Cond1 => {\n"
"        Type   => 'and',\n"
"        Fields => {\n"
"            StateID => {\n"
"                Type  => 'String',\n"
"                Match => '1',\n"
"            },\n"
"            DynamicField_Marke => {\n"
"                Type  => 'String',\n"
"                Match => 'VW',\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"    Cond2 => {\n"
"        Type => 'and',\n"
"        Fields => {\n"
"            Queue => {\n"
"                Type  => 'String',\n"
"                Match => 'Raw',\n"
"            },\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"},\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2506
msgid "Let's look at the condition configuration in detail."
msgstr "让我们看看这个条件配置的详细信息。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2509
msgid "Type (Condition)"
msgstr "类型（条件）"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2511
msgid ""
"Specifies the way the different condition elements are connected to each "
"other. Possible values:"
msgstr "指定不同的条件元素互相连接的方式，可能的值有："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2516
msgid ""
"<literal>and</literal>: This is the default. All conditions must be met for "
"the transition to take effect."
msgstr ""
"<literal>and（与）</literal>：这是默认值。 必须满足所有条件才能使转换生效。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2522
msgid "<literal>or</literal>: At least one condition must match."
msgstr "<literal>or（或）</literal>：至少有一个条件必须匹配。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2527
msgid "<literal>xor</literal>: Exactly one condition must match, not more."
msgstr "<literal>xor（异或）</literal>：必须只匹配一个条件，没有其它条件匹配。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2534
msgid "Cond1"
msgstr "Cond1"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2536
msgid ""
"This is the name of an example condition. It can be freely chosen.  "
"Conditions are evaluated in sorted order."
msgstr ""
"这是一个示例条件的名称。可以随便选择条件名称，条件按排好的顺序进行评估。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2541
msgid "Type (Cond)"
msgstr "类型（条件内字段）"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2543
msgid ""
"Specifies the way how the individual field tests of this condition are "
"connected to each other. Possible values:"
msgstr "指定这个条件内单个字段的测试结果互相连接的方式，可能的值有："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2548
msgid ""
"<literal>and</literal>: This is the default. All field tests must match for "
"this condition to match."
msgstr ""
"<literal>and（与）</literal>：这是默认值。 所有字段的测试必须都匹配此条件才能"
"匹配。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2554
msgid "<literal>or</literal>: At least one field test must match."
msgstr "<literal>or（或）</literal>：至少有一个字段测试必须匹配。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2559
msgid "<literal>xor</literal>: Exactly one field test must match, not more."
msgstr "<literal>xor（异或）</literal>：必须只匹配一个字段测试，没有其它匹配。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2568
msgid ""
"Specifies the particular fields whose values should be tested. From our "
"example:"
msgstr "指定要测试其值的特殊字段。在我们的例子中："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2573
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Fields => {\n"
"    StateID => {\n"
"        Type  => 'String',\n"
"        Match => '1',\n"
"    },\n"
"                        "
msgstr ""
"Fields => {\n"
"    StateID => {\n"
"        Type  => 'String',\n"
"        Match => '1',\n"
"    },\n"
"                        "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2582
msgid "StateID"
msgstr "StateID"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2584
msgid "Example of a field name. The following ticket fields can be used:"
msgstr "字段名的例子。可以使用下列工单字段："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2588
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    Title\n"
"    State\n"
"    StateID\n"
"    Priority\n"
"    PriorityID\n"
"    Lock\n"
"    LockID\n"
"    Queue\n"
"    QueueID\n"
"    Customer\n"
"    CustomerID\n"
"    CustomerNo\n"
"    CustomerUserID\n"
"    Owner\n"
"    OwnerID\n"
"    Type\n"
"    TypeID\n"
"    SLA\n"
"    SLAID\n"
"    Service\n"
"    ServiceID\n"
"    Responsible\n"
"    ResponsibleID\n"
"    DynamicField_$FieldName # for all DynamicFields\n"
"                        "
msgstr ""
"    Title\n"
"    State\n"
"    StateID\n"
"    Priority\n"
"    PriorityID\n"
"    Lock\n"
"    LockID\n"
"    Queue\n"
"    QueueID\n"
"    Customer\n"
"    CustomerID\n"
"    CustomerNo\n"
"    CustomerUserID\n"
"    Owner\n"
"    OwnerID\n"
"    Type\n"
"    TypeID\n"
"    SLA\n"
"    SLAID\n"
"    Service\n"
"    ServiceID\n"
"    Responsible\n"
"    ResponsibleID\n"
"    DynamicField_$FieldName # for all DynamicFields\n"
"                        "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2615
msgid ""
"When testing a field with 'ID' (like SLAID), the database ID of the field "
"will be used for testing, for other fields (like SLA) the actual value is "
"used for testing."
msgstr ""
"当测试一个含有‘ID’（如SLAID）的字段时，这个字段的数据库ID将用于测试，而其它字"
"段则使用实际值来测试。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2623
msgid "Determines the kind of field testing. Possible values:"
msgstr "确定字段测试的类型，可能的值有："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2628
msgid ""
"<literal>String</literal>: Compares the field value with the string "
"specified in <literal>Match</literal>. Matches if they are exactly the same."
msgstr ""
"<literal> String（字符串） </literal>：将字段值与<literal> Match（匹配） </"
"literal>中指定的字符串进行比较，如果它们完全一样则匹配。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2634
msgid ""
"<literal>Hash</literal>: Compares the field value (hash) with the hash "
"specified in <literal>Match</literal>. All hash values must be the same."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Hash（哈希）</literal>：将字段值（hash）与<literal> Match（匹配） </"
"literal>中指定的哈希进行比较，所有哈希值必须相同。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2640
msgid ""
"<literal>Array</literal>: Compares the field value (array) with the array "
"specified in <literal>Match</literal>. Both lists must be the same."
msgstr ""
"<literal> Array（数组） </literal>：将字段值（数组）与<literal> Match（匹"
"配） </literal>中指定的数组进行比较， 两个列表必须相同。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2646
msgid ""
"<literal>Regex</literal>: The field value can be tested with a regular "
"expression. It is important that <literal>Match</literal> contains "
"<emphasis>qr{}xms</emphasis> as a base condition. Between the braces the "
"actual regular expression can be noted."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Regex（正则表达式）</literal>：可以使用正则表达式测试字段值。 重要的"
"是，<literal> Match（匹配） </literal>包含<emphasis> qr {} xms </emphasis>作"
"为基础条件，在大括号之间才是实际的正则表达式。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2654
msgid ""
"<literal>Module</literal>: Allows you to use a perl module for condition "
"checking. If it returns 1, the check was positive. You can find an example "
"module in <filename>Kernel/System/ProcessManagement/TransitionValidation/"
"ValidateDemo.pm</filename>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Module（模块）</literal>：允许使用perl模块进行条件检查。 如果返回1，"
"检查结果是正的。 您可以在<filename>Kernel/System/ProcessManagement/"
"TransitionValidation/ValidateDemo.pm</filename>中找到一个示例模块。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2669
msgid ""
"Transition Actions are actions which can be triggered after successfully "
"applied transitions (when a process ticket moves from one activity to "
"another). These Transition Actions can be used to perform different changes "
"on the ticket, e. g.  change the Queue or the Owner of the ticket, and you "
"can also create your own Transition Actions to perform other complex changes."
msgstr ""
"转换操作是成功应用转换后触发的操作（当一个流程工单从一个活动移动到另一活动"
"时）。这些转换操作用来对工单执行不同的变更，如变更工单的队列或所有者，你还可"
"以创建你自己的转换操作来执行其它的复杂变更。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2676
msgid "Transition Action configuration"
msgstr "转换操作配置"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2682
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Queue Move',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketQueueSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Queue  => 'Junk',\n"
"            UserID => 123,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Queue Move',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketQueueSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Queue  => 'Junk',\n"
"            UserID => 123,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2698
msgid "The name of the Transition Action."
msgstr "转换操作的名称。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2702
msgid "Module"
msgstr "Module（模块）"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2704
msgid "Specifies the Perl module to be used."
msgstr "指定使用的Perl模块。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2708
msgid "Config"
msgstr "Config（配置）"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2710
msgid ""
"This parameter contains all settings which are required for the module. Its "
"content depends on the particular Transition Action module which is used. "
"Please see the documentation of the individual modules for details. In our "
"example, only the Queue must be specified. Nevertheless we are also sending "
"UserID parameter, by using the UserID parameter. The transition action will "
"be executed impersonating the user with the given UserID."
msgstr ""
"这个参数包含模块所需的所有设置。它的内容取决于使用的特定的转换操作模块。请参"
"阅单独的模块文档以了解详细信息。在我们的示例中，仅需指定队列，不过我们还需使"
"用UserID来发送UserID参数，转换操作将使用给定的UserID来模拟用户执行。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2718
msgid ""
"The use of UserID inside the <literal>Config</literal> parameter of a "
"Transition Action is accepted by all Transition Actions (since OTRS 3.2.4). "
"In this example it could be particularly important if the user that triggers "
"the Transition does not have permissions to move the ticket to the queue "
"<literal>Junk</literal>, while the user with the UserID 123 might have."
msgstr ""
"从OTRS 3.2.4开始，所有的转换操作都可以使用<literal> Config（配置） </literal>"
"参数中的UserID。 在本示例中，如果触发转换的用户没有权限将工单移动到队列"
"<literal> Junk </literal>，而UserID 为123的用户可能具有此权限，这是非常重要"
"的。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2726
msgid "Reusing Transition Action modules"
msgstr "重复使用转换操作模块"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2728
msgid ""
"To use Transition Action modules multiple times, just specify several "
"Transition Actions in your configuration. Example:"
msgstr "要重复使用转换操作模块，只需在配置中指定多个转换操作。例如："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2733
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    $Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"        'TA1' => {\n"
"            Name   => 'Queue Move Junk',\n"
"            Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketQueueSet',\n"
"            Config => {\n"
"                Queue => 'Junk',\n"
"            },\n"
"        },\n"
"        'TA2' => {\n"
"            Name   => 'Queue Move Raw',\n"
