"<literal>ForceNotificationToUserID</literal>、"
"<literal>ExcludeNotificationToUserID</literal>和"
"<literal>ExcludeMuteNotificationToUserID</literal>用于分别指定始终会通知的"
"UserID列表、不通知的UserID列表和列出但实际不发送通知电子邮件的UserID列表。"

