"在ACL的帮助下，你可以在流程工单中限制可选择的值。另请参阅<link linkend=\"acl-"
"reference\">ACL参考</link>以获取全部工单ACL语法的描述。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3403
msgid "ACL configuration"
msgstr "ACL 配置"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3405
msgid ""
"ACLs can only be defined in <filename>Kernel/Config.pm</filename>. Example:"
msgstr "只可以在文件<filename>Kernel/Config.pm</filename>中定义ACL。例如："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3409
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-ProcessProperties'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Process => {\n"
"            ProcessEntityID        => ['P1'],\n"
"            ActivityEntityID       => ['A1'],\n"
"            ActivityDialogEntityID => ['AD1'],\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-ProcessProperties'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Process => {\n"
"            ProcessEntityID        => ['P1'],\n"
"            ActivityEntityID       => ['A1'],\n"
"            ActivityDialogEntityID => ['AD1'],\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3428
msgid "001-ACL-ProcessProperties"
msgstr "001-ACL-ProcessProperties"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3430
msgid ""
"Name of the ACL rule. For further information on ACL rules in general, "
"please consult <link linkend=\"acl\">the ACL manual</link>."
msgstr ""
"ACL规则的名称。ACL规则的更多的信息，请查阅<link linkend=\"acl\">ACL手册</"
"link>。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3437
msgid ""
"This is the section that is used to check if an ACL must be applied. If it "
"has the specified values, the rule is applied. The following values can be "
"used:"
msgstr ""
"这部分用于检查是否必须应用一个ACL。如果指定了值，就是应用了ACL规则，可以使用"
"下列值："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3441
msgid "ProcessEntityID"
msgstr "ProcessEntityID 流程实体ID"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3443
msgid ""
"The ID of a process that the process. Matches if the ticket is assigned to "
"this process."
msgstr "一个流程的ID，如果工单分配到这个流程，则匹配成功。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3448
msgid "ActivityEntityID"
msgstr "ActivityEntityID 活动实体ID"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3450
msgid ""
"The ID of the Activity that the process ticket currently is assigned to."
msgstr "流程工单目前分配的活动的ID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3454
msgid "ActivityDialogEntityID"
msgstr "ActivityDialogEntityID 活动对话框实体ID"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3456
msgid ""
"The ID of the Activity Dialog that is currently open for a process ticket."
msgstr "一个流程工单目前打开的活动对话框的ID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3461
msgid "Possible/PossibleNot Activity Dialog"
msgstr "可能的/不可能的 活动对话框"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3463
msgid ""
"Here you can specify a list of Activity Dialog IDs. This list will limit the "
"possible Activity Dialogs that are offered to the user in the ticket zoom "
"mask."
msgstr ""
"在这里你可以指定活动对话框ID清单。这个清单限制了在工单详情屏幕提供给用户的可"
"用活动对话框。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3467
msgid ""
"<literal>Possible</literal> lists the Activity Dialogs that are allowed. The "
"setting above will only allow <literal>AD1</literal> and <literal>AD3</"
"literal> of the list of configured Activity Dialogs."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Possible</literal>列出允许的活动对话框。上述设置只允许配置的活动对话"
"框列表中的<literal> AD1 </literal>和<literal> AD3 </literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3471
msgid ""
"<literal>PossibleNot</literal> lists the Activity Dialogs that are not "
"allowed. In the example above, the setting will remove <literal>AD3</"
"literal> from the list of configured Activity Dialogs."
msgstr ""
"<literal>PossibleNot</literal>列出不允许的活动对话框。上述设置会从配置的活动"
"对话框列表中移除<literal>AD3</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3476
msgid ""
"If both <literal>Possible</literal> and <literal>PossibleNot</literal> are "
"specified, the list of configured Activity Dialogs will first be filtered by "
"<literal>Possible</literal>, leaving only <literal>AD1</literal> and "
"<literal>AD3</literal> in our example. Then <literal>PossibleNot</literal> "
"will be applied and filter out <literal>AD3</literal>, so that only "
"<literal>AD1</literal> remains and is shown as a possible Activity Dialog "
"that the user can use."
msgstr ""
"如果同时指定了<literal>Possible</literal>和<literal>PossibleNot</literal>，首"
"先通过<literal>Possible</literal>来过滤配置的活动对话框，在我们的示例中仅留"
"下 <literal>AD1</literal> 和<literal>AD3</literal>。然后应用"
"<literal>PossibleNot</literal>过滤掉<literal>AD3</literal>，所以最终只有"
"<literal>AD1</literal>保留下来作为用户可以使用的活动对话框。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3483
msgid ""
"If multiple ACL rules match, the intersection of all matching rules will be "
"calculated to determine the possible Activity Dialogs. Example:"
msgstr ""
"如果匹配了多个ACL规则，则计算所有匹配规则的交集来确定可能的活动对话框。例如："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3487
msgid ""
"Configured Activity Dialogs: <literal>AD1</literal>, <literal>AD2</literal>, "
"<literal>AD3</literal>, <literal>AD4</literal>, <literal>AD5</literal>, "
"<literal>AD6</literal>, <literal>AD7</literal>."
msgstr ""
"已配置的活动对话框：<literal>AD1</literal>、<literal>AD2</literal>、"
"<literal>AD3</literal>、<literal>AD4</literal>、<literal>AD5</literal>、"
"<literal>AD6</literal>、<literal>AD7</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3491
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-Status'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Status => 'new',\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'002-ACL-Queue'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Queue => ['Raw']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'003-ACL-Priority'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Priority => ['3 normal']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3', 'AD4'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-Status'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Status => 'new',\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'002-ACL-Queue'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Queue => ['Raw']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'003-ACL-Priority'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Priority => ['3 normal']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3', 'AD4'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3524
msgid ""
"If a process ticket has the state <literal>new</literal>, is in the "
"<literal>Raw</literal> queue and has a priority <literal>3 normal</literal>, "
"then all three ACL rules will match."
msgstr ""
"如果流程工单具有状态<literal> new </literal>，在<literal> Raw </literal>队列"
"中，并具有优先级<literal> 3 normal </literal>，则所有三个ACL规则都将匹配。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3528
msgid ""
"The first rule reduces the Activity Dialogs from <literal>AD1</literal>, "
"<literal>AD2</literal>, <literal>AD3</literal>, <literal>AD4</literal>, "
"<literal>AD5</literal>, <literal>AD6</literal>, <literal>AD7</literal> to "
"<literal>AD1</literal>, <literal>AD2</literal>, <literal>AD3</literal>, "
"<literal>AD6</literal>, <literal>AD7</literal> and forbids <literal>AD4</"
"literal> and <literal>AD5</literal>."
msgstr ""
"第一条规则将活动对话框从<literal>AD1</literal>、<literal>AD2</literal>、"
"<literal>AD3</literal>、<literal>AD4</literal>、<literal>AD5</literal>、"
"<literal>AD6</literal>、<literal>AD7</literal>减少为<literal>AD1</literal>、"
"<literal>AD2</literal>、<literal>AD3</literal>、<literal>AD6</literal>、"
"<literal>AD7</literal>，禁用了<literal>AD4</literal>、<literal>AD5</"
"literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3533
msgid ""
"The second rule will now further reduce the remaining Activity Dialogs.  In "
"our example, <literal>AD2</literal>, <literal>AD3</literal>, <literal>AD7</"
"literal> will remain."
msgstr ""
"第二条规则现在将进一步减少剩余的活动对话框。 在我们的示例中，<literal>AD2</"
"literal>、<literal>AD3</literal>、<literal>AD7</literal> 将保留下来。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3537
msgid ""
"Now the third rule will further reduce the list by <literal>PossibleNot</"
"literal>.  <literal>AD3</literal> is removed from the list. <literal>AD4</"
"literal> is not removed, since it was not on the list in the first place. At "
"the end, <literal>AD2</literal> and <literal>AD7</literal> remain as "
"possible Activity Dialogs that the user can utilize."
msgstr ""
"现在，第三条规则将通过<literal> PossibleNot </literal>进一步减少列表。 从列表"
"中删除<literal> AD3 </literal>。 <literal> AD4 </literal>未被删除，因为它不在"
"第一条规则的列表中。 最后，<literal> AD2 </literal>和<literal> AD7 </literal>"
"保留作为用户可以使用的活动对话框。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3543
msgid ""
"It is also possible to limit the processes that can be displayed in the "
"<literal>New process ticket</literal> screen. The functionality is similar "
"to limiting the Activity Dialogs with one exception: The ACLs could only be "
"based on Users."
msgstr ""
"还可以限制在<literal>新建流程工单</literal>屏幕中显示的流程。 功能类似于限制"
"活动对话框，除了一处不同：ACL只能基于用户。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3547
msgid "See examples below:"
msgstr "参阅下面的示例："

