"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/customers-and-groups.xml:42
msgid ""
"Customer Users can access the system by providing their username and "
"password. The CustomerID is needed by the system to identify the user and "
"associated tickets. Since the email address is a unique value, it can be "
"used as the ID."
msgstr ""
"客户用户可以通过提供用户名和密码访问系统。 系统需要CustomerID来识别用户和相关"
"的工单。 由于电子邮件地址是一个唯一的值，可以用作客户ID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/customers-and-groups.xml:46
msgid ""
"With the configuration parameter <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Setting_AdminCustomerUser::UseAutoComplete"
"\">AdminCustomerUser::UseAutoComplete</link> in the Admin SysConfig the "
"autocomplete field can be activated for the customer ID selection in the "
"customer user add or edit screen."
msgstr ""
"在系统管理系统配置中的<link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Setting_AdminCustomerUser::UseAutoComplete"
"\">AdminCustomerUser::UseAutoComplete</link>配置参数可以激活在添加或编辑客户"
"用户屏幕选择客户ID时的自动补齐功能。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/customers-and-groups.xml:51
msgid ""
"As with agents, groups and roles, customer users can not be deleted from the "
"system, only deactivated by setting the Valid option to <emphasis>invalid</"
"emphasis> or <emphasis>invalid-temporarily</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"与服务人员、组和角色一样，客户用户无法从系统中删除，只能通过将有效选项设置为"
"<emphasis>无效</emphasis>或<emphasis>临时无效</emphasis>来禁用。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/customers-and-groups.xml:58
msgid "Customer Users ↔ Customers Relations"
msgstr "客户用户↔客户的关系"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/customers-and-groups.xml:60
msgid ""
"Customer users can be assigned to multiple customers (and vice-versa) using "
"the link <emphasis>Customer Users ↔ Customers</emphasis> on the admin page. "
"In addition to their own (primary) customer, they will be linked to any "
"other customer for which there is a defined relation."
msgstr ""
"可以使用系统管理页面上的<emphasis>客户用户↔客户</emphasis>链接将客户用户分配"
"给多个客户（反之亦然）。 除了自己的（主要）客户之外，他们还将链接到与其定义了"
"关系的任何其他客户。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/customers-and-groups.xml:64
msgid ""
"This gives them access to tickets of customer users from these customers."
msgstr "这使他们能够访问这些客户的其它用户相关的工单。"

