#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/customers-and-groups.xml:129
msgid ""
"Customers can also be added to a group, which can be useful if you don't "
"want to add group relations to every single customer user. First create the "
"group to which your customers will belong, via the <link linkend=\"adminarea-"
"groups\">Group management module</link>. Then add the <link linkend="
"\"adminarea-queue\">queues</link> and select the new group for the queues."
msgstr ""
"如果你不想为每个客户用户添加组关系，也可以将客户添加到一个组中，这可能很有"
"用。 首先通过<link linkend=\"adminarea-groups\">组管理模块</link>创建客户所属"
"的组。 然后添加<link linkend=\"adminarea-queue\">队列</link>，并为该队列选择"
"新建的组。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/customers-and-groups.xml:133
msgid ""
"The next step is to activate the customer group support. This can be done "
"with the configuration parameter <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Setting_CustomerGroupSupport\">CustomerGroupSupport</"
"link>, from the Admin SysConfig option. Using the parameter <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Setting_CustomerGroupAlwaysGroups"
"\">CustomerGroupAlwaysGroups</link>, you can specify the default groups for "
"a newly added customers, so that every new customer will be automatically "
"added to these groups. Available permission levels can be changed via "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"下一步是激活客户组支持。 这可以通过系统管理-系统配置选项中的配置参数 <link "
"linkend=\"ConfigReference_Setting_CustomerGroupSupport\"> "
"CustomerGroupSupport（客户组支持）</link>完成。可以使用参数<link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Setting_CustomerGroupAlwaysGroups"
"\">CustomerGroupAlwaysGroups</link>指定新添加的客户的默认组，以便将每个新客户"
"自动添加到这些组。可以通过配置更改可用权限级别。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/customers-and-groups.xml:137
msgid ""
"Assigned permissions will be shared among all customer users of this "
"customer, so permissions don't have to be given individually to every "
"customer user (although this is still possible if required)."
msgstr ""
"分配的权限将在该客户的所有用户之间共享，因此不必为每个客户用户分配权限（尽管"
"如果需要，这仍然是可能的）。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/customers-and-groups.xml:141
msgid ""
"Different contexts of permission assignment are available, which will "
"determine how the permissions are inherited by customer users."
msgstr "权限分配的不同上下文是可用的，这将决定客户用户如何继承权限。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/customers-and-groups.xml:145
msgid "The following contexts are available:"
msgstr "下列的上下文可用："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/customers-and-groups.xml:150
msgid "Same Customer"
msgstr "同一客户"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/customers-and-groups.xml:152
msgid ""
"Group permissions will be inherited by all customer users of this customer. "
"This provides them with access to tickets of all customer users from the "
"this customer if they are located in a queue that's assigned to this group."
msgstr ""
"组权限将由该客户的所有用户继承。 如果他们位于分配给这个组的队列中，则可以让他"
"们访问来自该客户的所有用户的工单。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
