#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:495
msgid "Web Service Provider Network Transport"
msgstr "WEB服务提供都网络传输"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:497
msgid ""
"In future the list of available network transports will be increased. "
"Currently only <emphasis>HTTP::SOAP</emphasis> and <emphasis>HTTP::REST</"
"emphasis> transports are available. Each transport has different "
"configuration options to setup and they might use different frontend modules "
"to configure them."
msgstr ""
"将来可用的网络传输列表可能会增加，目前只有“<emphasis>HTTP::SOAP</"
"emphasis>”和“<emphasis>HTTP::REST</emphasis>”传输可用。每个传输有不同的配置选"
"项，并且可能使用不同的前端界面来配置它们。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:503
msgid ""
"It is quite simple to configure the <emphasis>HTTP::SOAP</emphasis> protocol "
"as provider.  There are only two settings: <emphasis>Namespace</emphasis> "
"and <emphasis>Maximum message length</emphasis>. These fields are required. "
"The first one is a URI to give SOAP methods a context, reducing ambiguities, "
"and the second one is a field where you can specify the maximum size (in "
"bytes) for SOAP messages that OTRS will process."
msgstr ""
"配置“<emphasis>HTTP::SOAP</emphasis>”作为提供者很简单。只有两个设"
"置“<emphasis>命名空间</emphasis>”和“<emphasis>消息的最大长度</emphasis>”。这"
"些字段是必填的，第一个是一个URI（统一资源标识符），为SOAP方法指定一个上下文，"
"减少歧义；第二个是你可以指定OTRS能够处理SOAP消息的最大尺寸（单位：字节）。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:511
msgid "Web service provider network transport (HTTP::SOAP)"
