msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/genericinterface/"
"genericinterface-webservice-provider-transport-soap.png\" scalefit=\"1\" "
"width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:518
msgid ""
"Optionally, you may want to define additional response headers. These may be "
"used to add static header values to every response. Just click on Add "
"response header and fill both key and value fields. There is no limit in "
"number of additional header lines."
msgstr ""
"或者，你可能需要定义附加的响应头，它们可用于为每个响应添加静态标头值。 只需点"
"击“添加响应头”并填充键和值字段。 附加的标头行的数量没有限制。"

