#. type: Content of: <section><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:6
msgid "Statistics"
msgstr "统计"

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:9
msgid ""
"The OTRS statistics module holds features to track operational statistics "
"and generates custom reports associated with OTRS usage. The OTRS system "
"uses the term \"statistic\" generically to refer to a single report "
"presenting various indicators."
msgstr ""
"OTRS统计模块支持跟踪操作的统计和生成定制的OTRS使用情况的报告的功能。OTRS系统"
"使用“统计”术语一般指一个呈现各种指标的报表。"

#. type: Content of: <section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:13
msgid ""
"For <ulink url=\"https://www.otrs.com/solutions/\"><emphasis role=\"bold"
"\">OTRS Business Solution™</emphasis></ulink> customers, there is also a "
"reports generator available. Here \"report\" refers to a collection of "
"several statistics in one PDF document that can be easily configured and "
"automatically generated and distributed. Please find more details in the "
"<ulink url=\"http://otrs.github.io/doc/manual/otrs-business-solution/stable/"
"en/html/index.html\"><emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution™</"
"emphasis> manual</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"对<ulink url=\"https://www.otrs.com/solutions/\"><emphasis role=\"bold"
"\">OTRS Business Solution™（OTRS商业解决方案）</emphasis></ulink> 的客户，还"
"有一个专用的报表生成器可用。这里的“报表”指在一个PDF文档中数个统计的集合，可以"
"轻松配置并自动生成和分发PDF文档。请在<ulink url=\"http://otrs.github.io/doc/"
"manual/otrs-business-solution/stable/en/html/index.html\"><emphasis role="
"\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution™</emphasis>（OTRS商业解决方案）手册</ulink>中"
"查找更详细的信息。"

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:18
msgid ""
"Proper configuration of the OTRS statistics module is associated with a "
"multitude of requirements and considerations. These include the various OTRS "
"modules to be evaluated, user permission settings, indicators to be "
"calculated and their complexity levels, ease of configuration of the "
"statistics module, speed and efficiency of calculations, and support of a "
"rich set of output variants."
msgstr ""
"OTRS统计模块的合理配置与大量的需求和考量相关，包括评估多种OTRS模块、用户权限"
"设置、计算指标及其复杂性级别、统计模块配置的易用性、计算的速度和效率以及支持"
"一组丰富的输出变量。"

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:22
msgid ""
"Statistical elements, i.e. files which supplement the functionality of the "
"statistics module for specific requirements, can be integrated for "
"calculating complex statistics."
msgstr ""
"统计的元素如文件（增补了统计模块特定需求的功能）可以集成来计算复杂的统计数"
"据。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:26
msgid "Statistics Configuration and Usage"
msgstr "统计配置和用法"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:29
msgid ""
"When signed on as an agent, the statistics module can be opened by selecting "
"\"Reports\" and then \"Statistics\" in the main menu."
msgstr ""
"作为服务人员登录时，可以通过选择主菜单中的“报表”和“统计”来打开统计模块。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:33
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概览"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:36
msgid ""
"Selecting the \"Statistics\" link in the navigation bar, and then the "
"submenu link \"Overview\", calls up the Overview screen. The Overview screen "
"presents a list of all pre-configured reports the agent can use (see figure "
"below)."
msgstr ""
"从导航栏选择“统计”然后点击子菜单“概览”可以调出概览屏幕。概览屏幕提供了该服务"
"人员能够使用的预配置报表的列表（见下图）。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:41
msgid "Overview of the standard statistics."
msgstr "标准统计概览。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:43
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-overview.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-overview.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:49
msgid ""
"When the statistics module is installed, it comes preloaded with a few "
"sample statistics imported into the system. These are shown as a list on the "
"overview page. If the overview list extends to more than a single page, the "
"agent can browse through the different pages. The list of statistics can be "
"sorted as desired, by clicking the desired column header in the list. To "
"generate a particular statistic, click on the statistic's \"Run now\" link."
msgstr ""
"统计模块安装后，它预先加载了导入到系统中的一些示例统计，这些统计在概览屏幕显"
"示为一个列表。如果单个列表扩展为多面显示的列表，服务人员可以在不同的页面切换"
"浏览。点击列表上期望排序的列标题，统计列表可以按期望排序。要生成一个特定的统"
"计，在这个统计上点击“立即运行”链接即可。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:54
msgid "Generation"
msgstr "生成统计"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:57
msgid ""
"The view user interface provides the stat's configuration settings (see "
"figure below)."
msgstr "查看统计界面提供了统计的配置设置（见下图）。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:62
msgid "Viewing a specific statistic."
msgstr "查看一个特定的统计。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:64
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-view.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-view.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:70
msgid ""
"Configuration settings for a particular statistic can be set within the "
"range of options in the View screen. Either the statistic creator or any "
"others with the appropriate permissions can make the settings."
msgstr ""
"可以在编辑屏幕设置一个特定统计有限的配置选项。统计创建者或其它有合适权限的人"
"员可以编辑这些设置。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:74
msgid ""
"Pressing the \"Start\" button (at the bottom of the screen) is the last step "
"to generate the statistic."
msgstr "点击“立即运行”按钮（在屏幕左侧）可以生成这个统计。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:82
msgid ""
"Agents with write rights can edit an existing report configuration by "
"calling up the edit user interface of the statistics module. Alternately, "
"they may create a new report."
msgstr ""
"有写入权限的服务人员可以在统计模块的编辑界面编辑一个已有的报表配置。另外，他"
"们也可以创建一个新的报表。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:86
msgid ""
"There are four possible steps in the configuration of a statistic: the "
"general specification data, configuring the x-axis, y-axis and possible data "
"filters for the reported data (or restrictions).  Let's create a new "
"statistic as an example by clicking the \"Add\" button in the overview "
"screen.  Our goal will be to get an overview of how many tickets with very "
"high priority are in every queue (x-axis) and state (y-axis)."
msgstr ""
"配置一个统计有4个可能的步骤：一般预设数据、配置X轴、配置Y轴和可能的报表数据过"
"滤器（或限制）。让我们创建一个新的示例统计，在概览屏幕点击“添加”按钮。我们的"
"目标是获取每个队列（X轴）和每个状态（Y轴）有多少工单优先级是非常高的列表。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:94
msgid "Adding a new statistic, first step."
msgstr "添加一个新的统计，第一步。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:96
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-add-typeselection."
"png\" scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-add-typeselection."
"png\" scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:102
msgid ""
"At the beginning we have to select the type of statistic we want to add. "
"Three types are available:"
msgstr "在开始页面我们必须选择要添加的统计的类型。有3个可用的类型："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:108
msgid "Dynamic Matrix Statistics"
msgstr "动态矩阵统计"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:111
msgid ""
"This type of statistics will generate a matrix of computed values (e.g. new "
"tickets per day of month and queue).  All value cells in the matrix have the "
"same type (number, average time, etc.).  Values are computed from entities "
"in the system (e.g. tickets).  Some matrix statistics support a summation "
"column and/or row (only useful for certain data)."
msgstr ""
"这个类型的统计会生成一个计算值的矩阵（例如：月度和队列每天的新工单）。矩阵中"
"所有的单元格值类型相同（数字、平均时间等等）。值通过系统中的条目（例如：工"
"单）计算而来。一些矩阵统计支持一个汇总列和/或汇总行（只对某些数据有用）。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:119
msgid "Dynamic List Statistics"
msgstr "动态列表统计"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:122
msgid ""
"This kind of statistic will generate a table where every line (not cell) "
"represents an entity in the system (e. g. a ticket).  The columns in this "
"row are usually configurable (x-axis, see below) and contain the data of "
"this object (e. g. ticket attributes).  All value cells in one column have "
"the same type."
msgstr ""
"这种统计会生成一个表格，表格的每一行（不是单元格）代表系统中的一个实体（例"
"如：一个工单），这一行的每列通常是可以配置的（X轴，见下）并包含这个对象的数据"
"（例如：工单属性）。一列的所有单元格值的类型相同。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:129
msgid "Static Statistics"
msgstr "静态统计"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:132
msgid ""
"This kind of statistic is not very much configurable and usually used for "
"very special and/or complex computations."
msgstr "这种统计很少配置，通常用于非常特殊和/或复杂的计算。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:106
msgid "<placeholder type=\"variablelist\" id=\"0\"/>"
msgstr "<placeholder type=\"variablelist\" id=\"0\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:140
msgid ""
"So let's select \"Dynamic Matrix\" for our example. Then the \"General "
"Specifications\" configuration will appear below the statistic type "
"selection."
msgstr ""
"所以在本示例中让我们选择“动态矩阵”。然后在统计类型下会出现“一般设定”的配置。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:144
msgid "Adding a new statistic, second step."
msgstr "添加一个新的统计，第二步。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:146
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-add-general.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-add-general.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:151
msgid ""
"After providing a title and description for the new statistic, we have to "
"select the statistics backend that we want to use.  This is the actual "
"backend module which is responsible to collect and analyze the data for our "
"statistic.  In our case we'll select \"TicketAccumulation\"."
msgstr ""
"提供新统计的标题和描述后，我们必须选择要使用的统计后端。这是负责收集和分析统"
"计数据的实际后端模块。在我们的例子中我们选择“TicketAccumulation（累积工"
"单）”。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:156
msgid ""
"By configuring permission groups, we can facilitate a restriction of the "
"groups (and therefore, agents) who can later view and generate the pre-"
"configured statistics. Thus the various statistics can be allocated to the "
"different departments and work groups who need them. It is possible to "
"allocate one statistic to various groups."
msgstr ""
"通过配置权限组，我们能够促进谁可以在后面查看和生成预配置的统计的组限制（也就"
"是服务人员）。所以可以给需要统计的不同部门和工作组分配多个不同的统计。也可以"
"将一个统计分配给多个组。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><example><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:160
msgid "Default statistics permission group"
msgstr "默认统计权限组"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><example><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:162
msgid ""
"The \"stats\" group was selected. The report is viewable for all users "
"having at least ro rights for the \"stats\" group. This access is available "
"by default."
msgstr ""
"选择“stats”组，对“stats”组至少有‘只读’权限的用户均可查看这个报表。这个访问权"
"限是默认可用的。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><example><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:168
msgid "Customized statistics permission group"
msgstr "定制统计权限组"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><example><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:170
msgid ""
"A group named \"sales\" was selected. All users with ro rights for the "
"\"sales\" group can see the stat in the view mode and generate it. However, "
"the report will not be available for viewing by other users."
msgstr ""
"选择一个名为“sales”的组，对“sales”组有‘只读’权限的用户均可查看并生成这个报"
"表。但是其它用户无法查看这个报表。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:175
msgid ""
"Additionally, possible output formats can be selected. Here we can just keep "
"all output formats and choose the one to use when actually generating the "
"statistic. Let's save the statistic now."
msgstr ""
"此外，还可以选择输出格式。在这里我们只需保持所有输出格式并在实际生成统计时再"
"选择一个输出格式。现在让我们保存这个统计。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:179
msgid ""
"The next screen will indicate the next step with a highlighted button: we "
"should configure the x-axis. By clicking the button, a dialog will appear "
"where we can select the element to be used for the x-axis. In our case that "
"will be the queue:"
msgstr ""
"“保存”统计后会出现下一个屏幕：配置X轴。点击“X轴”按钮，出现一个对话框，我们可"
"以选择用于X轴的元素。在我们的例子中就是‘队列’："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:185
msgid "Configuring the x-axis of a statistic."
msgstr "配置一个统计的X轴。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:187
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-config-xaxis.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-config-xaxis.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:193
msgid ""
"We can optionally limit the queues to be shown by selecting some in the "
"queue field. With the checkbox we can control if the agent who generates the "
"statistic can make changes to the queue selection.  We'll keep the defaults "
"and press \"Save\"."
msgstr ""
"通过在队列字段选择一些队列，我们可以随意地限制要显示的队列。通过复选框我们能"
"够控制服务人员生成统计时是否可以修改选择的队列。我们保持默认并点击“保存”按"
"钮。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:198
msgid ""
"Now we can configure the y-axis in the same way: select the state field."
msgstr "现在我们可以通过相同的方法配置Y轴：选择‘状态’字段。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:203
msgid "Configuring the y-axis of a statistic."
msgstr "配置一个统计的Y轴。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:205
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-config-yaxis.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-config-yaxis.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:211
msgid ""
"Here it is possible to select one element or two. In the first case, every "
"value of the element will be one element on the y-axis. If two elements are "
"selected, their permutations will be the elements on the value series.  For "
"example you could select \"state\" and \"priority\", and the resulting "
"elements will be \"new - 1 very low\", \"new - 2 low\", ... \"open - 1 very "
"low\" and so on. Let's just use the state and press \"Save\"."
msgstr ""
"在这里可以选择一个或两个元素。一个元素时，元素的每个值就是Y轴的一个元素。如果"
"选择了两个元素，它们的排列就是值系列（Y轴）的元素。例如你可以选择“状态”和“优"
"先级”，结果元素就是“新建-1-非常低”、“新建-2-低” ... “处理中-1-非常低”等等。让"
"我们仅使用“状态”并点击“保存”。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:217
msgid ""
"Now in the last step we could add data filters to only report tickets "
"belonging to a certain customer, with certain priorities and so on. We'll "
"add a filter for very high priority tickets:"
msgstr ""
"现在最后一步，我们可以添加数据过滤器以便只统计属于某个客户某个优先级等条件的"
"工单。我们添加一个‘非常高’优先级的工单过滤器："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:223
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:240
msgid "Configuring the data filter of a statistic."
msgstr "配置一个统计的数据过滤器。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:225
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-config-filter.png"
"\" scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-config-filter.png"
"\" scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:231
msgid "Now press \"Save\" again. The configuration is finished."
msgstr "现在再次点击“保存”按钮，配置就完成了。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:234
msgid ""
"You may already have noted that in the configuration dialog there is a "
"preview area where we can check the effect of our configuration settings."
msgstr ""
"你可以已经注意到了，在配置对话框有一个统计预览区域，我们可以在这里检查配置设"
"置的效果。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:242
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-config-preview.png"
"\" scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-config-preview.png"
"\" scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:249
msgid ""
"Please note that the preview uses random data and does not consider data "
"restrictions."
msgstr "请注意预览使用的是随机数据且没有考虑数据过滤器。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:254
msgid ""
"The statistic is configured. By pressing the \"Run now\" button we can go to "
"the View screen where the desired output format can be selected and the "
"statistic can be generated in the different formats."
msgstr ""
"统计已经配置好了，点击“立即运行”按钮，我们能够进入查看屏幕选择输出格式，统计"
"可以用不同格式生成。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:263
msgid ""
"The Import user interface can be accessed by pressing the \"Import\" button "
"on the Overview screen. \"rw\" permissions for the statistics module are "
"required."
msgstr ""
"可以通过点击统计概览屏幕的“导入”按钮访问导入界面，需要统计模块的“读写”权限。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:268
msgid "Statistics import"
msgstr "导入统计"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:270
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-import.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/administration/stats/stats-import.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:276
msgid ""
"Facilitates the import of reports, and when combined with the export "
"function of the module, is a very handy functionality.  Stats can be created "
"and tested conveniently on test systems, then imported into the production "
"system."
msgstr ""
"促进统计模块的报表导入与导出功能结合使用，是一个非常方便的功能。可以在测试系"
"统中方便地创建和测试统计，然后导入到生产系统。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:284
msgid "Statistics System Administration"
msgstr "统计系统管理员"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:287
msgid ""
"This section provides information about the tasks and responsibilities of "
"the OTRS administrator dealing with the statistics module."
msgstr "本部分提供系统管理员处理统计模块的任务和职责的信息。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:291
msgid "Permission settings, Groups and Queues"
msgstr "权限设置、组和队列"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:294
msgid ""
"The default configuration of the module registration gives all agents with "
"\"stats\" group permissions access to the statistics module."
msgstr "统计模块注册的默认配置给所有服务人员有“stats”组权限来访问统计模块。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:298
msgid "Access according to permission settings:"
msgstr "根据权限设置的访问："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:301
msgid "<emphasis>rw</emphasis>. Allows configuring statistics."
msgstr "<emphasis>rw（读写）</emphasis>，允许配置统计。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:302
msgid "<emphasis>ro</emphasis>. Permits generating pre-configured statistics."
msgstr "<emphasis>ro（只读）</emphasis>，允许生成预先配置的统计。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:307
msgid ""
"The OTRS administrator decides whether agents with the permission to "
"generate pre-configured reports are allocated ro rights in the \"stats\" "
"group, or if their respective groups are added in the module registration in "
"SysConfig."
msgstr ""
"OTRS系统管理员决定是将有权限生成预先配置的报表服务人员分配“stats”组的‘只读’权"
"限，还是将他们各自的组加入系统配置中的模块注册信息。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:312
msgid "SysConfig Settings"
msgstr "系统配置设置"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:314
msgid ""
"The SysConfig groups <link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Section_Core_Stats"
"\">Core::Stats</link> and <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Section_Frontend_Agent_View_Stats\">Frontend::Agent::View::"
"Stats</link> contain all configuration parameters for the basic set-up of "
"the statistics module. Moreover, the configuration parameter <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Setting_Frontend::Module_AgentStatistics\">$Self-&gt;"
"{'Frontend::Module'}-&gt;{'AgentStats'}</link> controls the arrangement and "
"registration of the modules and icons within the statistics module."
msgstr ""
"系统配置组<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Section_Core_Stats\">Core::Stats</"
"link> 和<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Section_Frontend_Agent_View_Stats"
"\">Frontend::Agent::View::Stats</link>包含统计模块基本设置的所有配置参数。 此"
"外，配置参数<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Setting_Frontend::"
"Module_AgentStatistics\">$Self-&gt;{'Frontend::Module'}-&gt;{'AgentStats'}</"
"link>控制模块的布置和注册，以及统计模块内的图标。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:319
msgid "Generating Statistics on the Command Line"
msgstr "用命令行生成统计"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:322
msgid ""
"Statistics can be generated on the command line with the command "
"<filename>bin/otrs.Console.pl Maint::Stats::Generate</filename>.  As an "
"example, see the command line call in the following script."
msgstr ""
"可以在命令行执行命令<filename>bin/otrs.Console.pl Maint::Stats::Generate</"
"filename>来生成统计。举个例子，查看下面脚本中的命令行调用。"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:327
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> bin/otrs.Console.pl Maint::Stats::Generate --number 10004 --target-directory /tmp\n"
"Generating statistic number 10004...\n"
"  Writing file /tmp/List_of_the_most_time-consuming_tickets_Created_2015-09-08_14-51.csv.\n"
"Done.\n"
msgstr ""
"shell> bin/otrs.Console.pl Maint::Stats::Generate --number 10004 --target-directory /tmp\n"
"Generating statistic number 10004...\n"
"  Writing file /tmp/List_of_the_most_time-consuming_tickets_Created_2015-09-08_14-51.csv.\n"
"Done.\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:336
msgid ""
"A report from the statistic configuration \"Stat#10004\" is generated and "
"saved as a CSV file in the <filename>/tmp</filename> directory."
msgstr ""
"从统计配置“Stat#10004”生成报表并保存为一个CSV文件到<filename>/tmp</filename>"
"目录。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:340
msgid ""
"The generated report can also be sent as an e-mail. More information can be "
"called up with the command in the script below."
msgstr "生成的报表还可以作为邮件发送，可以执行下面脚本中的命令获取更多信息。"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:344
#, no-wrap
msgid "shell> bin/otrs.Console.pl Maint::Stats::Generate --help\n"
msgstr "shell> bin/otrs.Console.pl Maint::Stats::Generate --help\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:350
msgid ""
"It usually does not make sense to generate reports manually via the command "
"line, as the statistics module has a convenient graphical user interface. "
"However, generating reports manually does make sense when combined with a "
"cron job."
msgstr ""
"通常通过命令行手动生成报表没有什么意义，因为统计模块有一个便利的图形界面。但"
"是，结合一个cron任务来手动生成报表就有意义了。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/stats.xml:354
msgid ""
"Imagine the following scenario: On the first day of every month, the heads "
"of department want to receive a report for the past month. By combining a "
"cron job and command line call the reports can be sent to them automatically "
"by e-mail."
msgstr ""
"想像下列场景:每月的第一天，部门领导要收到一份过去一月的报表。通过结合cron任务"
"和命令行生成报表可以通过邮件自动将报表发送给他们。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:9
msgid ""
"Appointment calendar feature provides a calendar implementation that allows "
"agents to manage and display multiple calendars and their appointments."
msgstr "预约日历功能允许服务人员管理和显示多个日历及其预约。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:13
msgid "Management of multiple calendars"
msgstr "管理多个日历"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:15
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:9
msgid "Via a management interface it is possible to add and edit calendars."
msgstr "通过管理界面，可以添加和编辑日历。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:18
msgid ""
"Beside calendar names, it is possible to assign colors and access groups, as "
"well as the current validity of the calendars."
msgstr "除日历名称之外，还可以指定颜色和访问组，以及日历的当前有效性。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:23
msgid "Exports and imports"
msgstr "导出和导入"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:25
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:108
msgid ""
"Once different calendars are created, it is possible to export either the "
"complete calendar definition (including the calendar appointments) in the "
"well-known YAML format or just export the related appointments of a calendar "
"to ICS format."
msgstr ""
"创建不同的日历后，可以用众所周知的YAML格式导出完整的日历定义（包括日历预"
"约），或仅将日历的相关预约导出为ICS格式。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:30
msgid ""
"It is also possible to import complete calendar structures using previously "
"exported YAML files to restore calendar definitions or import just calendar "
"appointments to an existing calendar using ICS file uploads."
msgstr ""
"还可以使用以前导出的YAML文件导入完整的日历结构，以恢复日历定义，或者通过上传"
"ICS文件将日历预约导入现有日历。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:35
msgid ""
"That offers the possibility to backup and restore single calendars or "
"transfer them to a different OTRS installation or an external calendar tool."
msgstr "这样可以备份和恢复单个日历或将其传输到其他OTRS安装环境或外部日历工具。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:40
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:331
msgid "Management of calendar appointments"
msgstr "管理日历预约"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:42
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:170
msgid ""
"If at least one calendar is created and accessible by a certain agent, new "
"or already existing appointments can be managed via a calendar overview and "
"an agenda overview."
msgstr ""
"如果至少有一个已经创建的日历且某些服务人员可以访问，则可以通过日历概览和日程"
"概览来管理新的或已经存在的预约。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:47
msgid ""
"Within the calendar overview, an agent is able to display, create, edit and/"
"or delete appointments of different calendars, depending on their permission "
"level to the related calendars. Such appointments can be created or edited "
"via drag and drop within this screen."
msgstr ""
"在日历概览中，服务人员可以根据相关日历的权限级别显示、创建、编辑和/或删除不同"
"日历的预约。 可以在此屏幕中通过拖放来创建或编辑此类预约。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:53
msgid ""
"The visibility of single calendars can be enabled or disabled through the "
"calendar list within the screen."
msgstr "可以通过屏幕中的日历列表启用或禁用单个日历的可见性。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:57
msgid ""
"To have a good overview of available appointments within different calendars "
"and the related dates they start or end, it is possible to select different "
"view modes, like weekly view, monthly view, different timeline related views "
"etc."
msgstr ""
"要在不同的日历和预约开始或结束的相关日期之间有一个很好的概览，可以选择不同的"
"视图模式，如每周视图、每月视图、不同的时间轴相关视图等。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:62
msgid ""
"Within the agenda overview, an agent is able to display the appointments of "
"all available (accessible) calendars in a table-like overview. This overview "
"is designed to have a detailed list of upcoming appointments in a structured "
"table. Like in the calendar overview, appointments can be created, edited or "
"deleted. This view supports a monthly, weekly and daily point of view on "
"available appointments."
msgstr ""
"在日程概览中，服务人员能够以类似表格的概览显示所有可用（可访问的）日历的预"
"约。 此概述旨在详细介绍结构化表中即将到来的预约。 像在日历概览中一样，可以创"
"建、编辑或删除预约。 这个视图支持每月、每周和每天视角的可用预约。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:70
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:416
msgid "Repeating appointments"
msgstr "重复预约"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:72
msgid ""
"If recurring appointments needs to be archived, it is possible to setup "
"detailed information about the occurrences of a single appointment."
msgstr "如果需要归档重复预约，可以设置有关单个预约发生的详细信息。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:76
msgid ""
"Beside pre-defined frequencies like daily, weekly, monthly etc. it is "
"possible to setup custom repeats and exclude weekdays or dates of months, "
"define the amount of recurrences and/or the end date after the appointment "
"stops to repeat."
msgstr ""
"除了每天、每周、每月等预先定义的频率外，还可以设置自定义重复，排除月份中的某"
"些工作日或日期，定义重复次数和/或预约停止重复后的结束日期。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:82
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:488
msgid "Notifications"
msgstr "通知"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:84
msgid ""
"Within the edit screen of an appointment, it is possible to setup a date to "
"notify about the appointment."
msgstr "在预约的编辑屏幕中，可以设置一个日期来通知预约。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:88
msgid ""
"As in the settings for appointment repeat, it is possible to use pre-defined "
"templates for notifications (i.e. 5 minutes before, 15 minutes before etc.) "
"or setup a custom point of time."
msgstr ""
"如在重复预约的设置中，可以使用预定义的模板进行通知（如5分钟之前、15分钟之前"
"等）或设置自定义时间点。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:93
msgid ""
"The custom settings for notifications allows to setup a relative point of "
"time (like 5 minutes after the appointment has been started) or an explicit "
"date/time expression."
msgstr ""
"通知的自定义设置允许设置相对时间点（例如预约开始后5分钟）或明确的日期/时间表"
"达式。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:99
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:518
msgid "Event-based appointment/calendar notifications"
msgstr "基于事件的预约/日历通知"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:101
msgid ""
"As in the well-known ticket notifications, this package comes up with an "
"event based notification mechanism, that can be handled using an "
"administration interface.  Within that interface, notification event entries "
"can be created, updated and/or deleted to react on different OTRS events "
"with related filters, recipients and content templates."
msgstr ""
"如同众所周知的工单通知，这个软件包提供了一个可以使用管理界面处理的基于事件的"
"通知机制。 在该界面中，可以创建、更新和/或删除通知事件条目，以响应具有相关过"
"滤器、收件人和内容模板的各种OTRS事件。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:108
msgid ""
"The content of notifications can be dynamically filled-up using OTRS smart "
"tags, like in the event based ticket notifications."
msgstr "可以使用OTRS智能标签动态填充通知内容，就如基于事件的工单通知一样。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:113
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:817
msgid "Managed ticket appointments"
msgstr "托管工单预约"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:115
msgid ""
"This package offers the possibility to automatically create and update "
"appointments in calendars based on ticket data, using special rules defined "
"within the calendar edit screen. Any ticket date/time value (i.e. pending "
"time, escalation times or dynamic fields) can be used to define appointment "
"start and end dates."
msgstr ""
"这个软件包提供了使用日历编辑屏幕中定义的特殊规则，根据工单数据在日历中自动创"
"建和更新预约的可能性。 可以使用任何工单日期/时间值（如挂起时间、升级时间或动"
"态字段）来定义预约开始和结束日期。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:122
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:749
msgid "Link tickets to appointments"
msgstr "链接工单到预约"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:124
msgid ""
"Within the edit screen of an appointment, it is possible link existing "
"tickets."
msgstr "在预约的编辑屏幕内，可以链接现有工单。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:127
msgid "Tickets can be searched by their ticket numbers and/or titles."
msgstr "工单可以通过他们的工单编号和/或标题进行搜索。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:130
msgid ""
"Links between tickets and appointments appear in the ticket zoom like every "
"other linked objects in a related table."
msgstr ""
"工单和预约之间的链接与所有其他相关表格中的链接对象一样显示在工单详情屏幕。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:134
msgid ""
"Those links can either be created through an existing appointment, using the "
"overviews or via the link feature in the ticket zoom."
msgstr ""
"这些链接可以通过预约概览中的现有预约创建，也可以通过工单详情中的链接功能创"
"建。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:138
msgid ""
"It's also possible to create a new appointment out of the ticket zoom, which "
"links the related ticket automatically to the new appointment."
msgstr "也可以从工单详情中创建一个新预约，将相关的工单自动链接到新预约。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:143
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:1014
msgid "Dashboard widget for upcoming appointments"
msgstr "即将到来的预约的仪表板小部件"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:145
msgid ""
"Every agent can activate a dashboard widget <emphasis>Appointments</"
"emphasis> in the dashboard."
msgstr ""
"每个服务人员都可以在仪表板上激活<emphasis>预约</emphasis>仪表板小部件。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/introduction.xml:149
msgid ""
"This widget shows the upcoming appointments of the different calendars for "
"today, tomorrow and the next 5 days."
msgstr "这个小部件显示今天、明天和未来5天即将到来的日历预约。"

#. type: Content of: <section><title>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:5
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "用法"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:7
msgid "Calendar Management"
msgstr "日历管理"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:13
msgid "Calendar management overview"
msgstr "日历管理概览"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:15
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/appointment-calendar/calendarmanage-overview."
"png\" scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/appointment-calendar/calendarmanage-overview."
"png\" scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:20
msgid ""
"If a new calendar needs to be created or edited, it's necessary to define a "
"calendar name, a color and the permission group the calendar belongs to. "
"This is needed for agents to access the calendar properly with the related "
"permissions."
msgstr ""
"如果需要创建或编辑新的日历，则需要定义日历名称、颜色和日历所属的权限组。 服务"
"人员需要使用相关权限才能正确访问日历。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:26
