"other copyright notices."
msgstr "在其它版权声明附近为你所做的修正添加适当的版权声明。"

#. type: Content of: <appendix><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/fdl.xml:218
msgid ""
"Include, immediately after the copyright notices, a license notice giving "
