#. type: Content of: <chapter><title>
#: en/content/first-steps.xml:6
msgid "First Steps"
msgstr "OTRS第一步"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><abstract><para>
#: en/content/first-steps.xml:10
msgid ""
"The goal of this chapter is to provide a brief overview of OTRS and the "
"structure of its web interface. The terms 'agents', 'customers', and "
"'administrators' are introduced. We also login as the OTRS administrator and "
"take a closer look at the user preferences available on every account."
msgstr ""
"本章的目的是提供 OTRS 简短的概述及其 web 界面的结构，介绍术语‘服务人员’、‘客"
"户’和‘系统管理员’。还以 OTRS 系统管理员登录，仔细看看每个用户帐户可用的偏好设"
"置。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><title>
#: en/content/first-steps.xml:15
msgid "Agent Web Interface"
msgstr "服务人员WEB界面"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><note><para>
#: en/content/first-steps.xml:19
msgid ""
"Before logging on for the first time, please consider activating the HTTPS "
"on your web server in order for OTRS to be served as a secure app over SSL/"
"TLS protocol. For detailed instructions on how to do this, please consult "
"the documentation of your web server (e.g. Apache2)."
msgstr ""
"在第一次登录之前，请考虑激活Web服务器上的HTTPS，以便OTRS通过SSL/TLS协议提供安"
"全应用服务。 有关如何执行此操作的详细说明，请参阅Web服务器（如Apache2）的文"
"档。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><note><para>
#: en/content/first-steps.xml:24
msgid ""
"After you activate HTTPS, please set the configuration option "
"<literal>HttpType</literal> to <emphasis>https</emphasis> in <link linkend="
"\"adminarea-systemconfiguration\">SysConfig</link>. This will make sure that "
"all internal links in OTRS are indeed using HTTPS."
msgstr ""
"激活HTTPS后，请在<link linkend=\"adminarea-systemconfiguration\">系统配置</"
"link>中将配置选项<literal> HttpType </literal>设置为<emphasis> https </"
"emphasis>。 这将确保OTRS中的所有内部链接确实使用HTTPS。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><note><para>
#: en/content/first-steps.xml:29
msgid ""
"Good practice is to also redirect all HTTP traffic to HTTPS, in case someone "
"tries to access the OTRS via an insecure link. This should be done on web "
"server configuration level for maximum effect. However, in case this is not "
"possible, you can set <literal>HTTPSForceRedirect</literal> to "
"<emphasis>Yes</emphasis> in <link linkend=\"adminarea-systemconfiguration"
"\">SysConfig</link> to do it on application level."
msgstr ""
"好的做法是将所有HTTP流量重定向到HTTPS，以防有人试图通过不安全的链接访问"
"OTRS。 这应该在Web服务器的配置级别上进行，以实现最大效果。 但是，如果这不可"
"能，你可以在<link linkend=\"adminarea-systemconfiguration\">系统配置</link>中"
"将<literal> HTTPSForceRedirect </literal>设置为<emphasis>是</emphasis>，以便"
"在应用程序级别实现HTTPS。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><para>
#: en/content/first-steps.xml:37
msgid ""
"The agent web interface allows agents to answer customer requests, create "
"new tickets for customers or other agents, write tickets about telephone "
"calls with customers, write FAQ entries, edit customer data, etc."
msgstr ""
"服务人员WEB界面允许服务人员答复客户请求、为客户或其它服务人员创建新工单、创建"
"客户的电话工单、编写FAQ知识库条目、编辑客户信息数据等等。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><para>
#: en/content/first-steps.xml:41
