#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:194
msgid "Installing OTRS on a Red Hat Enterprise Linux or CentOS system"
msgstr "在Red Hat Enterprise Linux或CentOS系统上安装OTRS"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:197
msgid ""
"This section describes the installation of our RPM package on a Red Hat "
"Enterprise Linux (RHEL) or CentOS server."
msgstr ""
"本部分描述了在一台Red Hat Enterprise Linux (RHEL) 或 CentOS 服务器上RPM软件包"
"的安装。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:201
#: en/content/installation/source.xml:10
msgid "Preparation: Disable SELinux"
msgstr "准备：禁用SELinux"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:204
#: en/content/installation/source.xml:13
msgid ""
"If your system uses SELinux, you should disable it, otherwise OTRS will not "
"work correctly."
msgstr "如果你的系统使用了SELinux，你需要禁用它，否则OTRS无法正常工作。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:208
#: en/content/installation/source.xml:17
msgid "Here's how to disable SELinux for RHEL/CentOS/Fedora:"
msgstr "下面是如何在RHEL/CentOS/Fedora中禁用SELinux："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:212
#: en/content/installation/source.xml:21
msgid "Configure SELINUX=disabled in the /etc/selinux/config file:"
msgstr "在文件/etc/selinux/config中配置SELINUX=disabled："

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:215
#: en/content/installation/source.xml:24
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# This file controls the state of SELinux on the system.\n"
"# SELINUX= can take one of these three values:\n"
"#       enforcing - SELinux security policy is enforced.\n"
"#       permissive - SELinux prints warnings instead of enforcing.\n"
"#       disabled - No SELinux policy is loaded.\n"
"SELINUX=disabled\n"
"# SELINUXTYPE= can take one of these two values:\n"
"#       targeted - Targeted processes are protected,\n"
"#       mls - Multi Level Security protection.\n"
"SELINUXTYPE=targeted\n"
msgstr ""
"# This file controls the state of SELinux on the system.\n"
"# SELINUX= can take one of these three values:\n"
"#       enforcing - SELinux security policy is enforced.\n"
"#       permissive - SELinux prints warnings instead of enforcing.\n"
"#       disabled - No SELinux policy is loaded.\n"
"SELINUX=disabled\n"
"# SELINUXTYPE= can take one of these two values:\n"
"#       targeted - Targeted processes are protected,\n"
"#       mls - Multi Level Security protection.\n"
"SELINUXTYPE=targeted\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:231
#: en/content/installation/source.xml:40
msgid ""
"Reboot your system. After reboot, confirm that the getenforce command "
"returns <literal>Disabled</literal>:"
msgstr "重启系统。重启后确认命令getenforce返回为<literal>Disabled</literal>："

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:234
#: en/content/installation/source.xml:43
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> getenforce\n"
"Disabled\n"
msgstr ""
"shell> getenforce\n"
"Disabled\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:248
msgid ""
"You can use OTRS using different database back-ends: <application>MySQL</"
"application>, <application>PostgreSQL</application> or <application>Oracle</"
"application>. The most popular database to deploy OTRS on is MySQL.  This "
"chapter shows the steps you need to take to configure MySQL on a RHEL-based "
"server.  Of course you can install the database on a dedicated database "
"server if needed for scalability or other purposes."
msgstr ""
"你可以使用不同的数据库后端：<application>MySQL</application>、"
"<application>PostgreSQL</application>或<application>Oracle</application>。部"
"署OTRS最流行的数据库是MySQL。本节描述了在基于RHEL的服务器上配置MySQL需要的步"
"骤。当然如果你有伸缩性或其它方面的需要，也可以将数据库安装到一台单独的数据库"
"服务器上。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:254
msgid "Install MySQL (or MariaDB) by executing the following command as root:"
msgstr "以root用户执行下列的命令来安装MySQL（或MariaDB）："

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:258
#, no-wrap
msgid "shell> yum -y install mariadb-server\n"
msgstr "shell> yum -y install mariadb-server\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:264
msgid ""
"This will install MySQL with the default options on your system. You'll need "
"to change the defaults in order to make it suitable for OTRS. With a text "
"editor create a new file <filename>/etc/my.cnf.d/zotrs.cnf</filename> with "
"the following content:"
msgstr ""
"这会在你的系统上使用默认选项安装MySQL，你需要修改默认设置以适用于OTRS。使用文"
"本编辑器来创建一个新文件<filename>/etc/my.cnf.d/zotrs.cnf</filename>，包含如"
"下内容："

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:269
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[mysqld]\n"
"max_allowed_packet   = 64M\n"
"query_cache_size     = 32M\n"
"innodb_log_file_size = 256M\n"
msgstr ""
"[mysqld]\n"
"max_allowed_packet   = 64M\n"
"query_cache_size     = 32M\n"
"innodb_log_file_size = 256M\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:278
msgid ""
"Now execute <command>systemctl start mariadb</command> to re-start the "
"database server and activate these changes. Then run <command>/usr/bin/"
"mysql_secure_installation</command> and follow the on-screen instructions to "
"set a database root password, remove anonymous access and remove the test "
"database."
msgstr ""
"现在执行<command>systemctl start mariadb</command>来重启数据库服务器并激活刚"
"才的修改内容。然后运行命令<command>/usr/bin/mysql_secure_installation</"
"command>，并按照屏幕上的指令来设置数据库的root密码、移除匿名访问及删除test数"
"据库。"

