#. type: Content of: <section><title>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:6
msgid "OTRS on Windows"
msgstr "在Windows上使用OTRS"

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:9
msgid ""
"OTRS can be run on a wide range of system platforms, including Enterprise "
"Linux Platforms such as Red Hat Enterprise Linux, and SUSE Linux Enterprise "
"Server, as well as a series of other Linux derivatives."
msgstr ""
"OTRS可以在各种不同的系统平台上运行，包括企业级Linux平台如OTRS on Windows和"
"SUSE Linux Enterprise Server及一系列其它的Linux分支。"

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:12
msgid ""
"However, when running OTRS on Windows platforms we have encountered repeated "
"performance losses, and despite an exhaustive analysis, it has not been "
"possible to solve these issues to our satisfaction due to technical "
"differences. It is thus with a heavy heart that we have ceased development "
"on our Windows Installer and the OTRS Appliance due to the currently limited "
"availability of necessary third-party components offered by other vendors."
msgstr ""
"然而在Windows平台上运行OTRS时我们遭遇了反复的性能损失，尽管做过详尽的分析，但"
"是由于技术的差异，好像不可能解决这些性能问题到令人满意的程度。由于目前缺少其"
"他供应商提供的必要的第三方组件，因此带着一颗沉重的心,我们已经停止开发Windows"
"安装程序和OTRS Appliance（OTRS一体机，部署在虚拟机中无需安装可直接使用的OTRS"
"系统）。"

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:15
msgid ""
"Under these circumstances, we are not able to guarantee the continuing "
"operation of OTRS on Windows platforms, and therefore recommend migrating to "
"one of the Linux platforms mentioned above or recommend using our <ulink url="
"\"https://www.otrs.com/solutions/managed-otrs/\"><emphasis role=\"bold"
"\">OTRS Business Solution™</emphasis> Managed</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"在这些情况下，我们不能保证OTRS能持续地运行于Windows平台，所以推荐将OTRS迁移到"
"上面提及的Linux平台或使用我们托管的<ulink url=\"https://www.otrs.com/"
"solutions/managed-otrs/\"><emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business "
"Solution™（OTRS商业解决方案）</emphasis> </ulink>。"

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:18
msgid ""
"To make it easier for you to migrate from Windows to Linux and to offer you "
"the best OTRS performance, we have prepared detailed instructions for you "
"here."
msgstr ""
"为了更容易地将OTRS从Windows迁移到Linux以获得最佳性能，我们在这里为你准备了详"
"细的说明。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:22
msgid "How to migrate existing Windows installations to Linux"
msgstr "如何迁移现有的Windows安装到Linux"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:24
msgid "Introduction and preparation"
msgstr "说明和准备"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:26
msgid ""
"If you have a Windows based installation and you would like to change to a "
"Linux based system you will need to setup a Linux server or virtual machine "
"and install OTRS there (see <link linkend=\"installation\">the installation "
"instructions</link>). This will be the target system for the migration."
msgstr ""
"如果你有了一个基于Windows的OTRS安装并想迁移到Linux系统，你需要安装一台Linux服"
"务器或虚拟主机并在系统中安装OTRS（参阅<link linkend=\"installation\">安装说明"
"章节</link>），这将是迁移的目标系统。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:30
msgid "Get OTRSCloneDB script to clone databases"
msgstr "取得OTRSCloneDB脚本以克隆数据库"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:32
msgid ""
"Please go to the admin menu of the Windows based system and install the "
"newest version of OTRSCloneDB package into your OTRS:"
msgstr "进入Windows版的系统管理菜单，并安装最新版的OTRSCloneDB软件包到OTRS："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:35
msgid ""
"You can install the OTRSCloneDB package directly from the package manager. "
"Select \"OTRS Extensions\" from the dropdown list on the left and click on "
"the button \"Update repository information\" below. Then the OTRSCloneDB "
"package will be shown in a list where you can click on \"Install\"."
msgstr ""
"你可以从软件包管理器中直接安装OTRSCloneDB软件包。从左侧的下拉列表中选择“OTRS "
"Extensions”并点击“更新软件仓库信息”按钮，然后会在一个列表中显示OTRSCloneDB软"
"件包，点击“安装”即可。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:38
msgid ""
"You could also download the package manually from the OTRS FTP server and "
"install the package manually as described below.  <ulink url=\"http://ftp."
